006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.item;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.item.atomic.IAnyAtomicItem;
009import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.item.function.IArrayItem;
010import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.item.function.IMapItem;
011import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.item.node.INodeItem;
012
013import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
014
015public interface IItemVisitor {
016  /**
017   * Visit the array item instance.
018   *
019   * @param array
020   *          the instance to visit
021   */
022  void visit(@NonNull IArrayItem<?> array);
023
024  /**
025   * Visit the map item instance.
026   *
027   * @param map
028   *          the instance to visit
029   */
030  void visit(@NonNull IMapItem<?> map);
031
032  /**
033   * Visit the node item instance.
034   *
035   * @param node
036   *          the instance to visit
037   */
038  void visit(@NonNull INodeItem node);
039
040  /**
041   * Visit the atomic item instance.
042   *
043   * @param item
044   *          the instance to visit
045   */
046  void visit(@NonNull IAnyAtomicItem item);
047}
